<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men gāo xìng ér lái 迦南738</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men gāo xìng ér lái, wǒ men píng ān ér qù, yé hé huá shì wǒ men de bāng zhù.
 dà shān kě yǐ nuó kāi, xiǎo shān kě yǐ qiān yí, ài píng ān de yuē yǒng bù lí kāi.
 zài zhè qiān biàn wàn huà xū fú de shí dài lǐ, wǒ men gēn zhe bù biàn de yé sū.
 wǒ men bēn pǎo wǒ men chuán yáng, yé hé huá yào pài shǐ zhě dā jiù.
 hā lì lù yà hā lì lù yà. wǒ men huān hū chēng xiè yé hé huá.
 hā lì lù yà wǒ men zàn měi, tā shì wǒ men yǒng yuǎn de bāng zhù.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>738</hymn_number>
</song>